DTSTAMP:20260407T043741Z
DTSTART:20260407T173000Z
DESCRIPTION:Phinney Center\\\, Blue Building\\\, Room 7: This invigorating 
	HIIT-style exercise class promotes strength\\\, vitality\\\, and long-term
	 hormone health with a science-backed blend of targeted sculpting\\\, high
	-intensity cardio\\\, and functional movement training. This is a group fi
	tness class. Please bring a water bottle and an optional sweat towel. All 
	other equipment will be provided. \\nVital Sculpt HIIT meets every Tuesday
	 at 5:30 pm at the Phinney Center.\n\nhttps://www.phinneycenter.org/event/
	vital-sculpt-hiit-class-with-seattle-jazzercise/2026-04-07/\n\nFrom Phinne
	y Neighborhood Association (PNA)
URL:https://www.phinneycenter.org/event/vital-sculpt-hiit-class-with-seattl
	e-jazzercise/2026-04-07/
LOCATION:Phinney Center Campus: Blue (upper) Building\\\, 6532 Phinney Ave.
	 N.\\\, Seattle\\\, WA\\\, 98103\\\, United States
X-CALRIPPER-SOURCE:phinney-neighborhood-association
CATEGORIES:Phinney Neighborhood Association (PNA)
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
DURATION:PT1H
